Class WebsiteSpecificData

  • java.lang.Object
    • testCases.WebsiteSpecificData

  • public class WebsiteSpecificData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains initializations for all the configurable parameters of the framework which have been defined in the config.properties file and can be changed any time as the requirements maybe.

    Mehak Bains
